    public class RangingReadingLocated2D<S extends RadioSource>
extends RangingReadingLocated<S,​com.irurueta.geometry.Point2D>
    Contains a 2D located ranging reading associated to a given radio source (e.g. WiFi access point or bluetooth beacon), indicating the distance to such radio source.
